            </div>
            <div class="items twitter">
              <nobr style="display: flex; align-items: center">
                <img src="/img/logo/twitter.png" alt="twitter logo" />
                <a href="#"
                  >Connect to Twitter<br />
                  <span>(Feature Coming Soon)</span></a
